(2779, 691, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"7bb206ee\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9b13c49\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><strong>Office of the Regional Director<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\n<p><strong>The Office of the Regional Director<\\/strong> provides overarching leadership, policy direction, and administrative supervision to the National Commission on Muslim<br \\/>Filipinos (NCMF) Regional Office IX \\u2013 Zamboanga Peninsula. As the highest executive office within the regional structure, it ensures the faithful implementation<br \\/>of the Commission\\u2019s mandate pursuant to Republic Act No. 9997, and upholds the principles of public service, accountability, and cultural integrity in all<br \\/>regional operations.<br \\/>The Regional Director exercises authority over all divisions and units within the regional office, ensuring the efficient and coordinated delivery of programs<br \\/>and services related to socio-economic development, cultural preservation, Muslim civil registry support, legal affairs, Halal industry development, peace<br \\/>building and conflict resolution, and the facilitation of Hajj affairs. The office likewise oversees the formulation of regional plans, the monitoring and evaluation<br \\/>of program performance, and the alignment of regional initiatives with national priorities.<br \\/>Moreover, the Office of the Regional Director represents the Commission in all official engagements within the Zamboanga Peninsula, fosters strong<br \\/>interagency collaboration, and sustains partnerships with local government units, national government agencies, Muslim religious leaders, civil society<br \\/>organizations, and community stakeholders. Through strategic governance and principled leadership, the office remains committed to advancing the welfare,<br \\/>rights, and holistic development of Muslim Filipinos in the region.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\",\"text_color\":\"#1A1A1A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
