(3104, 670, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"7d5864f\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"69e04f7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h1>LEGAL AFFAIRS DIVISION (LAD)<\\/h1>\\n<div><br><\\/div>\\n<div><br><\\/div>\\n<p>The Legal Affairs Division (LAD) of the National Commission on Muslim Filipinos (NCMF) Regional Office IX \\u2013 Zamboanga Peninsula serves as the principal unit responsible for the provision of comprehensive legal services, advisory support, and policy guidance in the execution of the Commission\\u2019s mandate under Republic Act No. 9997. The division ensures that all programs, projects, and operations of the regional office adhere strictly to existing laws, regulations, and established governance standards, thereby upholding the principles of legality, accountability, and integrity in public service.<\\/p>\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\n<p>The division\\u2019s core responsibilities encompass the review, preparation, and monitoring of legal documents, contracts, memoranda, and agreements; provision of legal opinions and interpretations; and the development of internal policies and guidelines that strengthen the legal framework governing the operations of the regional office. Furthermore, LAD provides legal assistance to Muslim Filipinos in the region, particularly in matters relating to civil registry, family and personal status laws, property rights, inheritance, and other issues affecting the Muslim community.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\\n<p>LAD also represents the regional office in legal proceedings, coordinates with national government agencies and local authorities on matters of law, and facilitates compliance with judicial and quasi-judicial requirements. The division plays a vital role in ensuring that the programs and initiatives of NCMF <br>Regional Office IX are implemented in full accordance with the law, while protecting the rights, interests, and welfare of Muslim communities in the Zamboanga Peninsula.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#1A1A1A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
