than a meetingit is a renewed commitment to the Muslim Filipino communities we serve. As we move forward, I believe in inclusive leadership and empowering our frontliners to shape a more responsive NCMF, she stated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Participants also candidly raised concerns and suggestions during the open forum, fostering a healthy exchange of ideas and reaffirming the culture of trust and teamwork within the regional leadership.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The event concluded on a high note with shared optimism and a unified goal of improving the welfare, rights, and recognition of Muslim Filipinos in the Zamboanga Peninsula.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Regional Director\'s Corner', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '96-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-11-10 09:00:11', '2025-11-10 09:00:11', '', 96, 'http://localhost/ncmf-ro9/?p=288', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
