(309, 1, '2025-11-10 11:26:31', '2025-11-10 11:26:31', '<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost/ncmf-ro9/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/574076107_122128902692967033_1579002851094595095_n-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"The current image has no alternative text. The file name is: 574076107_122128902692967033_1579002851094595095_n.jpg\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In a quiet yet powerful moment of reflection and unity, <a></a>Regional Director Rhoaisa S. Matolo-Mukaram, JD, visited the Sadik Grand Mosque in Zamboanga City  one of the most beautiful symbols of Islam in the region. She was joined by Mr. Abdul Razzaq Siddiq, his beloved children, Dir. Cosanie Derogongan and his wife Dra. Princess Sabdullah, other dedicated employees, in what became a day of faith, gratitude, and renewed purpose.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As they stepped into the sacred halls of the mosque, hearts were lifted in remembrance of Allah (SWT)  the Most Merciful, the Most Compassionate. Surrounded by family and friends, RD Matolo-Mukaram reflected on the blessings of togetherness and the beauty of Islams message: that peace begins when hearts submit in humility and gratitude.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The visit was more than an act of worship; it was a reminder that leadership rooted in faith is leadership with compassion. It showed that beyond her duties as a public servant, RD Matolo-Mukaram is a mother, a believer, and a servant of Allah who draws strength from prayer and reflection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Indeed, faith binds people beyond borders  a Filipino and a Pakistani standing side by side in prayer, united by the same La ilaha illallah, Muhammadur Rasulullah. Such moments remind us that Islam transcends race, language, and culture, calling every believer to love, mercy, and service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>                    .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/ncmfzamboangapeninsula?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZX9qtDvMgflQzB8ROm4Tu2rAm9wJym-W-Vip_F0R1T-QLLt-0QHApN_RmgHMmIt3_rfmVLZuLZrh9XXwaZ9MXwqQ_z4DQWZuDkBKjtQLZaK9VaAQjof8_DpXrae4WaovHgNn92Px-vGIe3c7fkxFwhVVfQHqbuVxqhv3tHtSCSagw6aijpvNCSdD4G-qCl_B2G0oLbAYpbxNlv4bPgA2MKk&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#NCMFZamboangaPeninsula</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/newleadershipinaction?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZX9qtDvMgflQzB8ROm4Tu2rAm9wJym-W-Vip_F0R1T-QLLt-0QHApN_RmgHMmIt3_rfmVLZuLZrh9XXwaZ9MXwqQ_z4DQWZuDkBKjtQLZaK9VaAQjof8_DpXrae4WaovHgNn92Px-vGIe3c7fkxFwhVVfQHqbuVxqhv3tHtSCSagw6aijpvNCSdD4G-qCl_B2G0oLbAYpbxNlv4bPgA2MKk&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#NewLeadershipInAction</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/trabahokoibadahko?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZX9qtDvMgflQzB8ROm4Tu2rAm9wJym-W-Vip_F0R1T-QLLt-0QHApN_RmgHMmIt3_rfmVLZuLZrh9XXwaZ9MXwqQ_z4DQWZuDkBKjtQLZaK9VaAQjof8_DpXrae4WaovHgNn92Px-vGIe3c7fkxFwhVVfQHqbuVxqhv3tHtSCSagw6aijpvNCSdD4G-qCl_B2G0oLbAYpbxNlv4bPgA2MKk&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#TrabahoKoIbadahKo</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/publicservicewithaheart?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZX9qtDvMgflQzB8ROm4Tu2rAm9wJym-W-Vip_F0R1T-QLLt-0QHApN_RmgHMmIt3_rfmVLZuLZrh9XXwaZ9MXwqQ_z4DQWZuDkBKjtQLZaK9VaAQjof8_DpXrae4WaovHgNn92Px-vGIe3c7fkxFwhVVfQHqbuVxqhv3tHtSCSagw6aijpvNCSdD4G-qCl_B2G0oLbAYpbxNlv4bPgA2MKk&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#PublicServiceWithAHeart</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/sadikgrandmosque?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZX9qtDvMgflQzB8ROm4Tu2rAm9wJym-W-Vip_F0R1T-QLLt-0QHApN_RmgHMmIt3_rfmVLZuLZrh9XXwaZ9MXwqQ_z4DQWZuDkBKjtQLZaK9VaAQjof8_DpXrae4WaovHgNn92Px-vGIe3c7fkxFwhVVfQHqbuVxqhv3tHtSCSagw6aijpvNCSdD4G-qCl