(327, 1, '2025-11-14 09:00:28', '2025-11-14 09:00:28', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<h1><strong>NCMF Regional Office IX</strong>  <em>Zamboanga Peninsula</em></h1>\n<p></p>\n<p>The National Commission on Muslim Filipinos (<strong>NCMF</strong>) Regional Office IX serves the Muslim communities of the Zamboanga Peninsula, covering Zamboanga<br />City, Zamboanga del Sur, Zamboanga del Norte, and Zamboanga Sibugay. Guided by Republic Act 9997, the office implements NCMFs policies, programs,<br />and services to promote the welfare, rights, and development of Muslim Filipinos in the region.</p>\n<h2><br />Mandate</h2>\n<p>Preserve and develop the culture, tradition, institutions and well-being of Muslim Filipinos, in conformity with the country\'s laws and in consonance with<br />national unity and development.</p>\n<p><br />NCMF Regional Office IX is mandated to carry out the Commissions core functions in the region, including socio-economic development, cultural<br />preservation, Muslim civil registry support, legal assistance, Hajj operations, and peace-building efforts. The office ensures that national programs are<br />effectively delivered to local communities and that Muslim Filipinos have access to services that promote inclusivity and empowerment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Profile', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'profile', '', '', '2026-01-06 06:13:45', '2026-01-06 06:13:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ncmf-ro9/?page_id=327', 0, 'page', '', 0),
