(615, 1, '2026-01-06 06:09:15', '2026-01-06 06:09:15', '<p>The Socio-Cultural Program of NCMF Region IX is designed to promote, preserve, and develop the cultural and religious heritage of Muslim Filipino<br />communities. It focuses on:</p><ol><li>Madrasah Education and Shariah Programs<ul><li>Provides institutional support and development for madrasah education.</li><li>Implements Shariah programs and organizes Quran competitions to enhance religious learning and spiritual growth.</li></ul></li><li>Cultural Heritage and Community Development<ul><li>Promotes, develops, and manages Muslim cultural centers and heritage sites.</li><li>Supports the observance of Muslim holidays, festivities, and cultural services to strengthen community identity and pride.</li></ul></li></ol><p>*Pics<br />*List/ Directory of Masjid and Madrasa<br />*List/ Directory of Muslim Cultural Center and Heritage sites<br />*List of Muslim Holidays<br />(TO FOLLOW)</p>', 'Socio Cultural', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '546-revision-v1', '', '', '2026-01-06 06:09:15', '2026-01-06 06:09:15', '', 546, 'http://localhost/ncmf-ro9/?p=615', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
