(716, 1, '2026-01-06 06:48:58', '2026-01-06 06:48:58', '<h1>ADMIN AND FINANCE DIVISION (AFD)</h1><p></p><p>The Administrative and Finance Division (AFD) of the National Commission on Muslim Filipinos (NCMF) Regional Office IX  Zamboanga Peninsula serves as <br />the principal unit responsible for the comprehensive management of administrative and financial affairs of the regional office. The division is entrusted with ensuring the efficient, transparent, and accountable administration of resources, personnel, and logistical operations in accordance with existing laws, rules, and regulations, including government auditing standards and financial management protocols.</p><p></p><p>The divisions functions encompass the preparation, allocation, and monitoring of the regional offices budget; management of disbursements and financial records; oversight of procurement, property, and inventory management; and provision of general administrative support to all divisions and units within the regional office. Through these responsibilities, the AFD guarantees that programs, projects, and activities of the regional office are operationally feasible, financially sound, and aligned with the strategic objectives of the Commission.</p>', 'Admin and Finance Division (AFD)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '668-revision-v1', '', '', '2026-01-06 06:48:58', '2026-01-06 06:48:58', '', 668, 'http://localhost/ncmf-ro9/?p=716', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
